<br>
I play EQ to have fun.<br>
  <br>
Items breaking = not fun.<br>
Fixing equipment = not fun.<br>
Paying UberTradeskiller01 = not fun.<br>
Clicking combine 1000 times = not fun. (impossible for me since I have an RSI)<br>
Timesinks = not fun.<br>
<br>
Why would I ever want to waste time on these things when I could be xp'ing/raiding instead? I'd rather log and go do something fun/productive IRL.<br>
<br>
